<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q43_v4" title="Q43_v4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      La distancia <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math>, en metros, que recorre un carrito que parte del reposo en un riel de laboratorio está dada por el modelo
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>d</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mi>a</m:mi>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:msup>
              <m:mi>t</m:mi>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            </m:msup>
          </m:mrow>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>,
      donde <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> es el tiempo en segundos y <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi></m:math> es la aceleración en <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>s</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>
      En un experimento se observa que, a los 4 segundos, el carrito ha recorrido 32 metros. ¿Cuál es el valor de la aceleración <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi></m:math>?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">2<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">4<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>. El resultado coincide exactamente con los 32 metros observados.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">8<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>128</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>64</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>64</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">16<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>16</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>256</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>128</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>128</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>, esta opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir el modelo</strong></p>
            <p>La distancia recorrida está dada por:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>d</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                      <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                      <m:msup>
                        <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                      </m:msup>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los datos del problema</strong></p>
            <p>Se sabe que a los 4 segundos el carrito ha recorrido 32 metros, es decir:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>d</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>.
            </p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                      <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                      <m:msup>
                        <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                      </m:msup>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular la potencia</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:msup>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msup>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces la ecuación queda:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                      <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                      <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                      <m:mn>16</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Despejar la aceleración</strong></p>
            <p>Dividimos ambos lados por 8:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mfrac>
                    <m:mn>32</m:mn>
                    <m:mn>8</m:mn>
                  </m:mfrac>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La aceleración del carrito es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>